div.div: 移除Linux兼容的简单日志宏和类，添加Windows和Linux下创建目录的支持

Add cross-platform support and configuration for iconv
- Introduced a new configuration header (config.h.in) for cross-platform compatibility, supporting both Windows and Unix-like systems. - Updated localcharset.h to conditionally define DLL export/import macros based on the platform. - Refactored test files to include platform-specific headers and functionality, ensuring compatibility with both Windows and Linux environments. - Implemented simple logging macros and a logger class for Linux compatibility. - Adjusted console output settings and system commands to work seamlessly across platforms. - Ensured consistent handling of pause functionality in tests for both Windows and Linux.
更新.gitignore以包含.idea目录，修复UniConv.h中的宏定义格式，优化UniConv.cpp中的编码转换实现
添加增强的错误处理适配器和便利方法，更新测试用例以验证新功能

增强UniConv编码转换的性能和错误处理
-增加了UNICONV_UNLIKELY的参数有效性检查，用于早期退出。 优化了图标描述符的缓存键构建。 -实现LRU缓存退出策略，管理iconv描述符缓存大小。 -介绍了基于编码特征估计输出大小的方法。 改进了编码转换过程中的错误处理，包括缓冲区大小和无效序列的特定情况。 -为编码转换增加了批处理能力。 增强了对缓冲池和iconv缓存使用情况的统计收集。

Refactor logging system headers and improve code formatting
- Updated include paths for logging system headers to remove redundant directory structure. - Reformatted member variable declarations for better readability in BaseLogOutput, BasicLogFormatter, and other classes. - Added missing #define _CRT_SECURE_NO_WARNINGS in relevant files to suppress warnings. - Improved consistency in method declarations and definitions across various log filter and output classes. - Enhanced thread safety by ensuring proper mutex usage in logging components. - Cleaned up unnecessary whitespace and comments for better code clarity.
